</div>
<div class="content" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <h3>
    Press Releases
  </h3>
  <button class="white" style="float: right; margin-top: -70px;">
    View All
  </button>
  <div style="border-top: 2px solid #D9D9D9; padding-top: 20px; height: 1px;"></div>
  <div id="press-release-collection">
    <div class="press-release">
      <div class="tags">
        <span class="tag">Data & Research</span>
        <span class="tag">Tools</span>
        <span class="tag">2023</span>
      </div>
      <div class="press-release-info">
        <h4>
          <a>In the face of homelessness crisis, advocates release citywide mapping tool to combat source of income discrimination</a>
        </h4>
        <p>
          Unlock NYC and Neighbors Together launch an interactive tool to map source of income discrimination in New York City.
        </p>
        <button class="black">
          Download PDF
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="press-release">
      <div class="tags">
        <span class="tag">Data & Research</span>
        <span class="tag">Tools</span>
        <span class="tag">2023</span>
      </div>
      <div class="press-release-info">
